fields.title: Mobile App for Local Farmers Market
fields.description: Develop a mobile application (iOS and Android) that connects local farmers with consumers. The app will allow farmers to list their products, set prices, and manage inventory. Consumers can browse products, place orders, and choose pickup locations or delivery options. The app will also include a payment gateway and a notification system for order updates and market news.
